descp2: bool, optional If True, only the parameters that were set to non-default values will be printed when printing an estimator. For example, ``print(SVC())`` while True will only print 'SVC()' while the default behaviour would be to print 'SVC(C=1.0, cache_size=200, ...)' with all the non-changed parameters.
